"{\"content\":{\"body\":\"## My search for an acre of escape\\n\\n[![Paul Greenberg](https://miro.medium.com/fit/c/56/56/1\\\\*tPfbBeQ23qMKUptWlw1FaQ.jpeg)](https://4fishgreenberg.medium.com/?source=post_page-----82252fbaae82-----------------------------------)\\n\\n![](https://miro.medium.com/max/1400/1\\\\*lvzvn8HdxUe8BXEsPxlZ5w.png)\\n\\n“Granite erratic, Dudmaston” by Richard Webb is licensed under CC BY-SA 2.0. To view a copy of this license, visit <https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-sa/2.0/?ref=openverse&atype=rich>\\n\\nIt was the rock that caught my eye. Dappled with lichen and lighted by the afternoon sun, it appeared to be the perfect place for contemplation. A spot where you could sit and write your novel, ponder your place in the universe, and perhaps reach some kind of equilibrium with the planet.\\n\",\"timestamp\":1640222084,\"title\":\"Is Anywhere Safe from Climate Change? - Paul Greenberg - Medium\"},\"digest\":\"h3uqVIABYK6BO0eo13UWqIZoE6cBD8Phdz14QT9c-iE\",\"authorship\":{\"contributor\":\"0xAAAB0EAF5F887cd79aB439C83cEfbA2792f4226f\",\"signingKey\":\"{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"fQpPiL6UUTL7iv9rPrJbhBkQQO5SvEo5CLXocNN2Knc\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"yQDAFgDsqbeCjL_eQrqGmS1gBswC70hcGMXEYu2Jkbc\\\"}\",\"signature\":\"QSGEDfVApKZ5kmV27gppCjiTeqVJODelL9xIMF-OLsnGEk5nxOgRRmSCHnOU28xZM8x_VtNtJGdGeWs3c3PKog\",\"signingKeySignature\":\"0xf80bf5e4b69adeb79ce648a0a23cef0d2917d568a8ce6e9c279da36f40d4fff1023b5f0839bb6346e4b691d02e35d3abf92a10e47e574b3988322b21727e22da1c\",\"signingKeyMessage\":\"I authorize publishing on mirror.xyz from this device using:\\n{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"fQpPiL6UUTL7iv9rPrJbhBkQQO5SvEo5CLXocNN2Knc\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"yQDAFgDsqbeCjL_eQrqGmS1gBswC70hcGMXEYu2Jkbc\\\"}\",\"algorithm\":{\"name\":\"ECDSA\",\"hash\":\"SHA-256\"}},\"nft\":{},\"version\":\"12-21-2020\",\"origi